dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nahiyat Muhayrijah wa shu'bat Qal'at Sukkar
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Muhayrijah section, Qal'at Sukkar region.] Alternate title: Liwa' al-Kut wa al-Muntafik: qada'ay al-Hayy wa Qal'at Sukkar: nahiyat Muhayrijah wa shu'bat Qal'at Sukkar. [al-Kut and al-Muntafik provinces: Al-Hayy and Qal'at Sukkar districts: Muhayrijah section, Qal'at Sukkar region. Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1931. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
